'''亞塞拜然大獎賽'''（{{lang-az|Azərbaycan Qran Prisi}}）是一場自{{F1|2017}}開始舉辦的[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]分站賽事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions-4|title=FIA Announces World Motorsports Council decisions|date=2016-11-30|publisher=Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130174153/http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions-4|archive-date=2016-11-30|access-date=2016-11-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=No German Grand Prix on F1 2017 calendar but Azerbaijan race is official|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/nov/30/german-grand-prix-f1-2017-calendar|accessdate=2016-11-30|work=The Guardian|agency=Reuters|date=2016-11-30|archive-date=2020-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622103036/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/nov/30/german-grand-prix-f1-2017-calendar/|dead-url=no}}</ref>這場大獎賽舉辦於[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]]首都[[巴庫|巴庫]]的[[巴庫市街賽道|巴庫市街賽道]]，這條賽道的[[2016年歐洲大獎賽|首場一級方程式賽車賽事]]為{{F1|2016}}的[[歐洲大獎賽|歐洲大獎賽]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/12/f1-2016-calendar-confirmed.html |title=FIA confirms 2016 calendar |work=Formula1.com |publisher=Formula One Management |date=2015-12-02 |accessdate=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2015-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203231526/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/12/f1-2016-calendar-confirmed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

